  "text": "Cell culture, proliferation curves, inhibition assays, immunoblotting, mass and protein measurement, colony size measurement, and spore viability Cell culture, proliferation curves in shaking culture, proliferation on lawns of bacteria, and nuclei counts were done according to [CITATION_1] . Comparison of extracellular AprA and CfaD by immunoblotting, measurement of mass and protein content, colony size measurement on bacterial lawns, and spore viability assays were done following [CITATION_2] . Silver staining of conditioned media was done following [CITATION_3] . rAprA and rCfaD inhibition assays were done following [CITATION_4] , except that cells were incubated with rAprA or rCfaD for 48 hours before measurement of cell density.",
